Package: otzi
Version: 2.2.3
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: nodejs (>= 20)
Recommends: nginx
Maintainer: Ötzi <noreply@github.com>
Description: Post-quantum multisig vault for OPNet Bitcoin L1 smart contracts
 Ötzi combines distributed key generation (DKG), threshold
 ML-DSA signing, wallet management, and OPNet transaction broadcasting
 into a single self-hosted operations interface. Supports declarative
 project manifests for custom contract operations.
Homepage: https://github.com/mwaddip/otzi
